"Field Tasking Manager empowers communities to map informal settlements, "
"public\n"
"            facilities, and local services for inclusive planning."
msgstr ""
"Field Tasking Manager کمیونٹیز کو غیر رسمی آبادیوں، عوامی سہولیات، اور "
